# learning_git
Common Issues & Fixes

Issue 1: Wrong Remote URL (# in URL)
Error:
fatal: https://github.com/Mohana412/Learning_GIT#/info/refs not valid
Fix:
git remote remove origin
git remote add origin https://github.com/Mohana412/Learning_GIT.git

Issue 2: Push Rejected (fetch first)
Error:
! [rejected] main -> main (fetch first)
Fix: GitHub has changes your local doesn't have. Pull first:
git pull origin main --allow-unrelated-histories
git push -u origin main

Issue 3: master vs main Branch Mismatch
Error: Local branch is 'master' but GitHub uses 'main'
Fix:
git branch -m master main

Issue 4: Git Not Installed on AWS EC2
Error:
bash: git: command not found
Fix (Amazon Linux 2023 uses dnf):
sudo dnf install git -y
git --version
git clone https://github.com/Mohana412/Learning_GIT.git
